{"tid":2040851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府：任何制裁都是雙刃劍 希望美國政府繼續維持對港經貿政策","createTime":"2020-05-29T00:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T05:23:00.000Z","uid":125168,"like":24,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"9830529295b865bbbaa6cb3a67c5f144f664d357","tid":2040851,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:48:27.000Z","msg":"港府強烈反對美國務院報告　指任何制裁都是雙刃劍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392597&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=43212c1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392597&h=31fa2961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392597</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】港府強烈反對美國國務院按《香港政策法》提交的報告內以偏概全的言論。<br />\n<br />\n港府指言論曲解特區和中央的憲制關係，污名化香港落實一國兩制，干預特區內部事務。報告內有關高度自治以及巿民自由被蠶食的指控毫無根據，對此表示遺憾，又指訂立港區國安法會令香港恢復穩定。<br />\n<br />\n政府指本港單獨關稅區地位由《基本法》賦予，港美關係中任何制裁都是雙刃劍，損害香港利益之餘，亦嚴重損害美國自身利益，希望美國政府繼續維持對港經貿政策。"},{"pid":"d689d8304409659159f9871c5ccc93324f7daba7","tid":2040851,"uid":346806,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"你講冇用<br />\n叫習近平出嚟講"},{"pid":"53cc6f8e0f0fe8bc51b27f309622215dc1781bdc","tid":2040851,"uid":125168,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"d689d8304409659159f9871c5ccc93324f7daba7","tid":2040851,"uid":346806,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"你講冇用<br />\n叫習近平出嚟講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:51:13.000Z","msg":"去到呢個地步叫小學生岀嚟都無用"},{"pid":"078e74f44e4900908f6c2610a241dc64041c1968","tid":2040851,"uid":127575,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"開始驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方向正確的"},{"pid":"79a79a50c2705172538